sentences.sentence: His height gives him an inbuilt advantage over his opponent.
sentences.translation: 他的身高成为他相对于对手的先天优势。

sentences.sentence: Inbuilt resistance to pests, weeds and disease.
sentences.translation: 本身具有抵抗害虫，杂草及疾病的能力。

sentences.sentence: The foot has its own inbuilt strength and support so why duplicate this.
sentences.translation: 人的脚部本身就是一个结构强健的支撑结构，鞋底的形状实际只是脚底弧度的翻版。
